com.oym.indoor

Class Floor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oym.indoor.Floor

  • public class Floor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class includes all the information regarding the Floor Items stored in Links. As well, it includes the UrlTileProvider to be used to overlap the indoor maps in the Google Map.
